node.text:
A place where the exterior and interior come together 🔄⁣
The outdoor furniture by @andreuworld is perfectly integrated in this incredible home. Wouldn't you love to lie down on that incredible sun bed and enjoy the views?⁣
⁣
⁣
📐 @sergiobonaquestudio 
📷  @geraldkiernan 
📍Valencia, Spain⁣
